# Comic Store Backend

## Setup Instructions
1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone <repository_url>

# Install dependencies: 
 npm install

# Set up MongoDB and run the project:
npm start
 
 ## Endpoints

POST /api/comics: Create a new comic book.

PUT /api/comics/

: Update an existing comic book.

DELETE /api/comics/

: Delete a comic book.

GET /api/comics: Get all comics with filtering, pagination, and sorting.

GET /api/comics/

: Get details of a specific comic book.

